{"tid":2200790,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"央視稱王金平赴廈門「求和」遭炮轟 影片下架  國民黨：陸不道歉杯葛論壇","createTime":"2020-09-13T09:07:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T09:07:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"285ac0f91bb20d3704c008f3dabee4df092bc390","tid":2200790,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09:07:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200913/HEFQEADXABAIBI4ZXZYZSFYY3Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200913%2FHEFQEADXABAIBI4ZXZYZSFYY3Y%2F&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513SEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=9a08f4bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200913%2FHEFQEADXABAIBI4ZXZYZSFYY3Y%2F&h=345761a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200913/HEFQEADXABAIBI4ZXZYZSFYY3Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n央視稱王金平赴廈門「求和」遭炮轟 影片下架 <br />\n國民黨：陸不道歉杯葛論壇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GJVfSI_NVI7YuJqsDYy-2D2fC_Y=/720x643/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/J7WEXIGMGJBIHKY6LB7RT7QWAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGJVfSI_NVI7YuJqsDYy-2D2fC_Y%3D%2F720x643%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJ7WEXIGMGJBIHKY6LB7RT7QWAU.jpg&h=2d6e8dab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■央視主持人曾稱王金平是向大陸求和，前晚改口稱有助兩岸交流。<br />\n<br />\n台海關係緊張之際，海峽論壇下周在福建廈門舉行，台灣立法院前院長王金平代表國民黨率團參加，但人還沒出發，大陸央視即貶稱王金平此次是到大陸求和。事件越演越烈，此番言論連藍營亦不滿，國民黨主席江啟臣昨強調，不接受求和說，促陸方道歉，黨內指明不道歉將拒參加論壇。為平息怨憤，涉事影片已被下架，央視主持也改口稱：「王金平率團訪大陸有助兩岸交流。」惟官方仍未就事件道歉。<br />\n<br />\n第十二屆「海峽論壇」9月19日在福建廈門市舉行，國民黨隆重其事派王金平任團長、現任黨秘書長李乾龍任副團長，率代表團參加。.........................<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gofuTaz3BEKXZLAUI6t2irYMgrk=/860x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XUMEBAVJFNGNXFRVVLCZ4UAOX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgofuTaz3BEKXZLAUI6t2irYMgrk%3D%2F860x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXUMEBAVJFNGNXFRVVLCZ4UAOX4.jpg&h=55c117f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■國民黨主席江啟臣直指不能接受央視的求和說法，並促請陸方道歉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6R9Fsio3EpojkftcU_IrXZGhSUI=/1286x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6KVJBELETJA2RHLQLIYBSWPPBI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6R9Fsio3EpojkftcU_IrXZGhSUI%3D%2F1286x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6KVJBELETJA2RHLQLIYBSWPPBI.jpg&h=80eb3026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■王金平海峽論壇之行，因央視評論「求和」論而蒙上陰影。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n節目改口稱訪問團助兩岸交流<br />\n<br />\n事件引起爭議，國民黨主席江啟臣展現強硬立場，昨在facebook直言：「我個人作為中國國民黨主席，完全無法接受。」他昨稍早前與前總統馬英九到台北宣傳反美豬公投時，也重申參加海峽論壇是交流，不是求和，非為參加而參加，並促請大陸方面道歉。江啟臣昨晚再度促陸方當事人道歉，至於是否取消參加海峽論壇，他稱不排除任何打算。國民黨黨務幹部也指，如果對岸沒有道歉，..............................<br />\n<br />\n隨着事件發酵，央視已將影片下架，主持人李紅前晚在《海峽兩岸》節目改口稱：「在島內政壇有一定份量的王金平，此時帶團參加海峽論壇，...............................<br />\n<br />\n民進黨發言人顏若芳表示，國民黨仍在妄想大陸給個道歉，..........................<br />\n<br />\n另外，國民黨昨發起反對瘦肉精豬肉進口公投，國民黨號召民眾支持，昨日全台同步舉辦第一階段聯署，希望兩天內完成1萬份以上聯署書。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"}]}